## ✨ What it does

| Step | Action |
|------|--------|
| 📄 Upload | Drop any PDF into the system |
| 🔍 Search | Semantic search finds the most relevant chunks |
| 🤖 Answer | Groq LLM generates a precise, grounded answer |
| ⚡ Cache | Redis caches repeated queries instantly |
| 📊 Evaluate | RAGAS scores every answer for quality |

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```
User
 │
 ▼
Streamlit UI  ──────────────────────────────────────────►  FastAPI
                                                              │
                    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┤
                    │                                         │
                    ▼                                         ▼
             Redis Cache                              RAG Pipeline
             (instant reply)                               │
                                                           │
                              ┌────────────────────────────┤
                              │            │               │
                              ▼            ▼               ▼
                          Ingestion    Chunking       Embeddings
                          (PDF/Web)    (Semantic)     (HF E5)
                                                          │
                                                          ▼
                                                    Qdrant Vector DB
                                                          │
                                                          ▼
                                                    Groq LLM (Llama 3.1)
                                                          │
                                                          ▼
                                                       Answer
                                                          │
                              ┌───────────────────────────┤
                              │                           │
                              ▼                           ▼
                         RAGAS Eval                   MLflow
                         (quality score)              (tracking)
```

