## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Tool | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| 🖥️ UI | Streamlit | User interface |
| ⚡ API | FastAPI | REST endpoints |
| 🔍 Vector DB | Qdrant | Semantic search |
| 🧠 Embeddings | HuggingFace E5 | Text → vectors |
| 🤖 LLM | Groq (Llama 3.1) | Answer generation |
| 💾 Cache | Redis | Speed up repeated queries |
| 📊 Evaluation | RAGAS | Answer quality scoring |
| 🧪 Tracking | MLflow | Experiment logging |
| 📈 Monitoring | Grafana + Prometheus | Live dashboards |
| ⏰ Orchestration | Apache Airflow | Automated pipelines |
| 🐳 Container | Docker | Service management |
| 🔄 CI/CD | GitHub Actions | Auto test & deploy |

