## 📊 RAGAS Evaluation Metrics

| Metric | Description | Target |
|--------|-------------|--------|
| Faithfulness | Answer grounded in retrieved chunks | > 0.75 |
| Answer Relevancy | Directly answers the question | > 0.70 |
| Context Recall | Right chunks were retrieved | > 0.65 |

